WEBVTT

1
00:00:02.670 --> 00:00:04.950
- I think one of the most
underrated AI features

2
00:00:04.950 --> 00:00:07.410
is the ability of large
language models like Gemini

3
00:00:07.410 --> 00:00:09.780
to really translate across
different languages.

4
00:00:09.780 --> 00:00:11.670
So my parents primarily speak Korean,

5
00:00:11.670 --> 00:00:13.080
I mostly speak English

6
00:00:13.080 --> 00:00:14.280
and I use translation tools

7
00:00:14.280 --> 00:00:15.480
like Google Translate all the time.

8
00:00:15.480 --> 00:00:16.740
Super useful.

9
00:00:16.740 --> 00:00:19.020
But LLMS can, in some cases,

10
00:00:19.020 --> 00:00:20.970
do a much better job conveying the tone

11
00:00:20.970 --> 00:00:23.100
and the spirit of what the
person was trying to say

12
00:00:23.100 --> 00:00:25.733
and express it in the language
that they can understand.